            "type": "text",
            "text": " pipe operator from the LangChain Expression Language (LCEL). Each component exposes a uniform ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Runnable",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "code"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " interface, so chains compose without glue code and execute synchronously, asynchronously, or with token streaming using the same invocation API."
